luxuriousRoom
You're entering the room when you're hearing a sound in the dark. You're looking in the direction and you see a fairy glaring at you like it was the first time it has seen anything that doesn't look like a plant in years. They thank you for saving them before telling you they know a legendary spell that is known to cure all diseases. You go back to your village, accompagnied by the fairy called Xiv and you are able to cure everyone ! THE END !
